headline: Hormel announces key leadership appointments in Retail Business Unit
summary: Jul. 23—Hormel Foods Corporation has announced two leadership appointments in its Retail Business segment. Paul Peil, a 35-year veteran with the company, has been promoted to the role of vice president of marketing for Fresh and Ready Meats and Christie Crouch joins the company as vice president of marketing for Snacking and Entertaining.
